CatDescriptText: Related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1960, pg. A9, reads: "D.I.'s Stage Another Triumph At Arena"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of seven D.I. members, left to right: Gloria Golden Grate, Ruby Young Buchanan, Doryce Griffin, Nellye Barron, Margaret Watson, Gay DeHall, and Juanita Drake, wearing full length long sleeved satin gowns with wide waistbands and light colored gloves, standing in interior for D.I.'s National Foundation benefit, another version
